Obianuju Blessing Okeke, onye a maara nke ọma dị ka Uju Okeke, bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri na ihe nkiri Naijirịa
O nwere ọrụ na Mission to No Where na The Barrister
A mụrụ Okeke na Anambra Steeti
Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na nka íhe nkiri na Mahadum Nnamdi Azikiwe
N'afọ 2012, ọ lụrụ onye ya na ya nọrọ ogologo oge, Melekh
Ememe nsọ́ ahụ mere na Saint Barth Anglican Church na Lagos.
N'afọ 2006, Okeke rụrụ ọrụ dị ka odibo na ihe nkiri egwu Teco Benson Mission to Nowhere
N'afọ 2007, ọ meriri ihe nrite maka Nest Upcoming Actress na African Movie Academy Awards (AMAA) maka ọrụ ya na fim ahụ.
N'afọ 2018, ngalaba ihe nkiri na ihe nkiri, Mahadum Nnamdi Azikiwe, Awka, Anambra State kwanyeere ya ugwu.
